OL,7,FHe was arrested at his home in London
OL,8,Fon Monday evening
OL,10,FLord Peter Mandelson has been arrested
OL,11,Fon suspicion of misconduct in public
OL,12,Foffice, police said.
OL,14,FTwo officers were seen entering his
OL,15,Fhome on Monday evening, with a third
OL,16,Fperson entering shortly after.
OL,18,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,19,Fsaid: "Officers have arrested a 72-
OL,20,Fyear-old man on suspicion of
OL,21,Fmisconduct in public office.
