OL,3,CLord Peter Mandelson arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,F"He was arrested at an address in
OL,8,FCamden on Monday, February 23 and has
OL,9,Fbeen taken to a London police station
OL,10,Ffor interview.
OL,12,F"This follows search warrants at two
OL,13,Faddresses in the Wiltshire and Camden
OL,14,Fareas."
OL,16,FFootage shows a plain-clothed police
OL,17,Fofficer leading Lord Mandelson out of
OL,18,Fa house.
