OL,7,FTwo of his properties were previously
OL,8,Fsearched by police in connection with
OL,9,Fthe allegations, which surfaced
OL,10,Ffollowing the US Department of
OL,11,FJustice's document dump related to
OL,12,FEpstein last month.
OL,14,FHis arrest comes days after Andrew
OL,15,FMountbatten-Windsor was arrested by
OL,16,FThames Valley Police on suspicion of
OL,17,Fmisconduct in public office.
